title: Win when it counts
author: VD
content_html:
Sure, I’m not happy about losing the season series to the Packers. But you know, the third time pays for all…. I actually like the Vikings chances against Philadelphia with an iffy TO, (like in the sense that they exist at all), and if Atlanta can polish off the Rams, they could make it to the big game. For all Mike Martz’s insanity, they are the NFC team that scares me the most right now.

31-17. UHHH-OOOOOOOH!
